{"text": "\u201cJust because you have the emotional range of a teaspoon doesn't mean we all have.\u201d", "author": {"name": "J.K. Rowling", "goodreads_link": "/author/show/1077326.J_K_Rowling"}, "tags": ["hermione"]}
