{"text": "\u201cBooks are the quietest and most constant of friends; they are the most accessible and wisest of counselors, and the most patient of teachers.\u201d", "author": {"name": "Charles William Eliot", "goodreads_link": "/author/show/4398096.Charles_William_Eliot"}, "tags": ["books", "friends", "reading", "teachers"]}
