{"text": "\u201cIf you were half as funny as you think you are, you'd be twice as funny as you really are.\u201d", "author": {"name": "H.N. Turteltaub", "goodreads_link": "/author/show/357657.H_N_Turteltaub"}, "tags": ["misattributed-cassandra-clare", "misattributed-jace"]}
